  "response": "As of the latest data, the best camera phone in the range of \u20b915,000 to \u20b918,000 in India often fluctuates due to frequent new releases and updates in technology. However, several models within this price range are known for their excellent camera performance:\n\n1. **Redmi Note 10 Pro**: Known for its 64 MP quad-camera setup which includes an ultra-wide lens and macro lens, providing versatile photography options.\n\n2. **Realme 8 Pro**: This phone features a 108 MP primary camera which is exceptional in this price range, offering high resolution and detailed shots.\n\n3. **Samsung Galaxy M32**: Comes with a 64 MP quad-camera setup delivering good photo quality, especially in well-lit conditions.\n\n4. **Poco X3 Pro**: With a 48 MP quad-camera system and various shooting modes, it\u2019s a strong contender in mid-range camera phones.\n\n5. **Oppo F19 Pro**: Known for its impressive camera features including AI Color Portrait, dual-view video, and a 48 MP main camera.\n\nFor the best choice, consider checking the latest reviews, comparisons, and user feedback as camera performance can vary based on software updates and individual preferences.",
